 2010-05532010-04-29EC,  HEALTH,  ,  ,  , 
ActCanadian Environmental Protection Act, 1999
SubjectOrder Adding Toxic Substances to Schedule I to the Canadian Environmental Protection Act, 1999
PrecisOrder Adding TOXIC SUBSTANCES TO SCHEDULE 1 TO THE CANADIAN ENVIRONMENTAL PROTECTION ACT, 1999, which will add Methyloxirane, Ethyloxirane, Naphthalene,Toluene diisocyanates (three substances referred to as “TDI”), 1,2-Benzenediol (referred to as “catechol”) and 1,4-Benzenediol (referred to as “hydroquinone).
